Niko-Agent
==========

Niko-Agent is an authorized derivative of the local pico codebase at commit
4adae0b21b7525ab7d6678689253aff20d291fdc.

Design references reviewed during development:

- Pony Code: https://github.com/xiawiie/pony-code (MIT)
- Bunny Byte: https://github.com/LISAooo1234/Bunny-Byte

Niko-Agent's original changes include the Niko public interface, centralized
sensitive-path protection, append-only session forks, token-confirmed Git-visible
workspace rollback, recovery journals, and cross-platform verification entrypoints.

